<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="vi">



<head>

    <meta charset="UTF-8">

    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <title>

        <%= book.title %> - Xem trước | ArvaLibrary

    </title>

    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>

</head>



<body class="bg-gray-50">

    <header class="bg-gray-900 text-white shadow-lg sticky top-0 z-10">

        <div class="flex items-center justify-between max-w-7xl mx-auto p-4">

            <a href="/" class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-400">ArvaLibrary</a>

            <div class="flex-grow max-w-md mx-4 hidden md:block">

                <form action="/search" method="GET" class="flex">

                    <input type="text" name="q" placeholder="Tìm kiếm..."
                        class="w-full p-2 text-sm text-gray-900 border border-gray-300 rounded-l-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-yellow-500 focus:border-yellow-500"
                        required>

                    <button type="submit"
                        class="p-2 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-yellow-600 rounded-r-lg hover:bg-yellow-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-yellow-500 transition duration-200">

                        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">

                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                                d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"></path>

                        </svg>

                    </button>

                </form>

            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                <a href="/contact" class="hidden sm:inline-block">
                    <button
                        class="text-sm font-medium py-2 px-4 rounded-lg flex items-center transition duration-200 bg-yellow-700 hover:bg-yellow-800 whitespace-nowrap">
                        Liên hệ
                    </button>
                </a>
            </div>

        </div>

    </header>



    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-4 sm:p-6">

        <a href="/book/<%= book.id %>" class="text-yellow-600 hover:text-yellow-700 flex items-center mb-6">

            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">

                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18">

                </path>

            </svg>

            Quay lại

        </a>



        <div class="bg-white shadow-xl rounded-xl p-6 md:p-10 mb-10">

            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start mb-8">

                <div class="md:flex-shrink-0 mx-auto md:mx-0">

                    <img class="w-40 h-64 object-cover rounded-lg shadow-xl" src="<%= book.cover_url %>"
                        alt="<%= book.title %>"
                        onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='https://placehold.co/160x256/94a3b8/ffffff?text=B%C3%ACa+s%C3%A1ch+khuy%E1%BA%BFt'">

                </div>

                <div class="flex-grow text-center md:text-left">

                    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-1">

                        <%= book.title %>

                    </h1>

                    <p class="text-xl text-yellow-600 font-semibold mb-3">

                        <%= book.author || 'Tác giả ẩn danh' %>

                    </p>

                    <p class="text-md text-gray-500">

                        Năm xuất bản: <span class="font-medium">

                            <%= book.publication_date || 'Không rõ' %>

                        </span>

                    </p>

                    <div class="flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start space-x-2 mt-2">

                        <span class="text-xl font-bold text-yellow-500">

                            <%= book.rating %> ⭐

                        </span>

                        <% if(book.is_vip) { %>

                            <span
                                class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 bg-red-500 text-white text-xs font-bold rounded-full">

                                VIP

                            </span>

                            <% } %>

                    </div>

                </div>

            </div>



            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3 border-t pt-4">Tóm Tắt Chi Tiết (Xem Trước)</h2>

            <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-base">

                <p>

                    <br>

                    <%= book.preview_content || 'Không có mô tả chi tiết từ hệ thống.' %>

                </p>

            </div>



            <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-red-100 border-l-4 border-red-500 text-red-700 rounded-lg shadow-md">

                <p class="font-bold mb-3 text-xl flex items-center">

                    ⚠️ Nội dung đã được rút gọn!

                </p>

                <p class="text-base">

                    Bạn muốn xem toàn bộ nội dung hãy liên hệ tới ArvaLibrary để đặt sách nhé!
                    Hotline (Zalo): 0337126684, Email: ArvaLibrary@gmail.com để liên hệ đặt sách
                </p>

            </div>



            <div class="text-center mt-6">

                <a href="/contact"
                    class="inline-block py-3 px-8 text-xl font-bold text-white bg-red-600 rounded-lg hover:bg-red-700 transition duration-300 shadow-xl">

                    Liên Hệ Ngay

                </a>

            </div>



        </div>

    </main>

</body>



</html>